      <title>随着伯南克提出替代方案，美联储的预测方法看起来越来越过时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/fed-s-forecasting-method-looks-increasingly-outdated-as-bernanke-pitches-new-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储陷入了一种看起来越来越有限的预测和公共沟通模式，尤其是在经济不断带来惊喜的情况下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/fed-s-forecasting-method-looks-increasingly-outdated-as-bernanke-pitches-new-way</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:42:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅希望重新夺回主动权，泽伦斯基欢呼美国的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局对美国众议院批准超过 600 亿美元的援助感到欢欣鼓舞，不过焦点正在转移到援助能够以多快的速度到达前线，以及该计划将如何改变基辅在对抗俄罗斯入侵的斗争中的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 11:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储首选通胀指标将支持降息耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员即将得到进一步确认，证明对抗通胀的进展已陷入停滞，这支持了基调的转变，将利率维持在比先前预期更长的时间内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
